data.descriptionEn: The MSQ Current Transformer converts a high primary current of 400/1000/2000 A to a secondary current of 5 A for measurement or protection purposes. Part of the MSQ series, it offers high reliability and is available in accuracy classes such as 0.5 or 1.0 depending on the variant. Operates at 50-60 Hz. The secondary burden (rated VA) is matched to maintain accuracy (e.g. 2.5 VA, 5 VA etc.). The device is designed with insulation suitable for voltages up to approximately 0.72 kV (depending on version).
